reviews.review_text: franklin's - brent piano check out brents 'piano' at the start of franklin's. wish he'd played more of that (with b-3) as opposed to the keyboard sound he frequently used that people have described as 'toylike' which is an adjective i wouldnt use but never the less was not a fan of either
1rst Hampton show This is a great show and only Brent's third show with the band. The truckin smokes and the Stella blue is very, very good.
